    dc:title="I haven't decided..."
    dc:identifier="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/100"
    dc:description="I haven't decided whether to vote this year or not but casting a vote actively indicates that in some way you endorse/support the policy, views and actions of the group you vote for. What if you want to state that..."
